  <lyrics>[V1]
 Cristojj janirar sarcasinjja
 Má ewjj jaytistojja.
 Evangeliopat khananchiri
 Sarañasataqui.
 
[C] 
 Khespiyatanacajj
 Janc'ac sarapjjañán,
 Tatit Jesusat yatiyiri
 Take marcanacar.
 
[V2]
 Tatitut parlañataquejja,
 Chekpach munasiñamp.
 Kollan Ajay ch'amampiraqui,
 Phokt' asiñasawa.
 
[V3]
 Khespiyatáña munirejja,
 Take juchanacap
 Tatitur arsusiñapawa,
 Jopar iyawsasin.
 
</lyrics></song>